sx.blah.discord.util

Enum LogMarkers

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<LogMarkers>
      • sx.blah.discord.util.LogMarkers
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Comparable<LogMarkers>, org.slf4j.Marker

    public enum LogMarkers
extends Enum<LogMarkers>
implements org.slf4j.Marker
    This class contains all the SLF4J log Markers used in the Discord4J logger. Each marker enum implements Marker and is named after the value of Enum.toString().
